# === .gitignore (monorepo root) ===
# STR-003: Sub-projects have their own .gitignore files (backend/.gitignore,
# frontend/.gitignore) that cover their own node_modules, dist, and .env files.
# This root-level file catches anything that slips through when running
# git commands from the monorepo root, and covers IDE / OS artifacts that
# neither sub-project gitignore would address.

# ─── Operating System ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ─── IDEs & Editors ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
*.swp

# ─── Environment files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Belt-and-suspenders over sub-project .gitignores.
# A .env accidentally created at the monorepo root must never be committed.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# ─── Node (root-level installs only) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# node_modules/ with no leading slash correctly matches at any depth — this
# is intentional, every sub-project's node_modules should be ignored.
#
# /package-lock.json (WITH a leading slash) anchors the pattern to the repo
# root ONLY. Without the leading slash, this pattern would also match
# backend/package-lock.json and frontend/package-lock.json — lockfiles that
# must stay committed for reproducible installs (see audit DEP section) and
# that CI's cache-dependency-path configuration depends on. A root-level
# package-lock.json should not normally exist in this monorepo (the project
# has no root-level package.json), but the rule is anchored defensively in
# case one is ever created by an accidental `npm install` at the repo root.
node_modules/
/package-lock.json

# ─── Build outputs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
dist/
build/
.turbo/

# ─── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
lerna-debug.log*
